title: Toadies Almost Complete Rarities Collection
description:
This is a collection of some hard to find tracks. it features only unreleased material, as you are still able to go out and buy most of their stuff (an I recommend it). anyways, there is the Feeler record (except for the tracks that ended up on HB/SA), some stuff from Slaphead, and Chatterbox, a Live version of the Feeler record, and various other things. Alot of (if not most) is MP3 sourced, and then i lazily transfered a lot of them to wav, not flac, sorry. A lot of the earlier records are incomplet, only because they are so fucking hard to piece together. here is the track list:
